
1. install qt into /opt/qt
    ref: http://svn.corp.qunar.com/svn/search-team/qcontent-deps/package/qt-everywhere-opensource-src-4.7.1

2. install icu4c, glog, protobuf, google-perftools into /opt/qcontent/
    icu4c-3_6-src.tgz
    glog-0.3.1.tar.gz
    protobuf-2.3.0.tar.gz
    google-perftools-1.6.tar.gz

3. install bzip, libmemcached, memcached, tokyocabinet with a mulmis patch, tokyotyrant into /opt/qcontent
    bzip2-1.0.5.tar.gz
    libmemcached-0.42.tar.gz
    libevent-1.4.13-stable.tar.gz
    memcached-1.4.5.tar.gz
    tokyocabinet-1.4.44-patched-mulmisc.tar.gz
    tokyotyrant-1.1.40.tar.gz
    tokyotyrant-perl-1.16.tar.gz


4. mpio msgpack msgpack-rpc into /opt/qcontent
    mpio.tar.gz
    msgpack-0.5.2.tar.gz
    msgpack-rpc-cpp.tar.gz

5. install OpenCV for thumb scale
    OpenCV-2.2.0.tar.bz2

6. install other tools: git squid haproxy  opencc into /opt/qcontent
    git-1.7.0.5.tar.gz
    haproxy-1.4.6.tar.gz
    opencc-0.1.2.tar.gz
    squid-3.1.6.tar.gz

7. install qwebvdom
    ref: http://svn.corp.qunar.com/svn/search-team/qcontent/trunk/qwebvdom/INSTALL

8. install qmake
    cd qcontent
    qmake
    sudo make install


install qt and qcontent complteted.

